00:10:44.400 --> 00:10:46.860
have found that back to
these first three things

00:10:46.860 --> 00:10:49.920
that we talked about,
relationships and retention,

00:10:49.920 --> 00:10:53.700
productivity and creativity,
are things that keep clients

00:10:53.700 --> 00:10:54.810
around longer.

00:10:54.810 --> 00:10:56.550
So even in a
downturn, people are

00:10:56.550 --> 00:10:58.140
spending on business travel.

